- Pleased to meet you, Youngho.
- Me, too

03:09.455 --> 03:12.015
What have you been doing?

03:12.091 --> 03:14.616
It's really him!

03:14.694 --> 03:17.197
- Welcome to hometown.
- You still remember me.

03:17.197 --> 03:21.156
- Of course we remember you.
- It's really been a long time.

03:22.268 --> 03:25.066
You remember this girl?

03:25.138 --> 03:27.674
Chong Oksun, who always
fell asleep during class.

03:27.674 --> 03:30.040
- How are you doing?
- This is Kim Mihwa with the frog lips.

03:30.143 --> 03:32.077
- It's Lee Mihwa.
- Lee Mihwa.

03:32.178 --> 03:34.544
Dr. Pimple, Shin Jongja.

03:34.614 --> 03:37.105
Now, the wife of the chief of
a bus company.

03:38.184 --> 03:39.208
Hi!

03:39.285 --> 03:41.276
Nice to meet you again.

03:42.922 --> 03:45.254
Let's have a seat and drink.

03:50.863 --> 03:56.358
- Hey.
- Sit down. Have a drink.

03:59.072 --> 04:01.666
We really wanted to contact you,

04:02.041 --> 04:05.602
but we couldn't.

04:05.945 --> 04:06.912
It's all right.

04:07.013 --> 04:10.972
I'm the one who should
be sorry for not calling you.

04:11.117 --> 04:15.577
This guy's the head
of our friendship association now.

04:15.688 --> 04:18.350
- Bongwoo club.
- Right, Bongwoo club.

04:18.591 --> 04:20.752
I am really sorry
for not contacting you.

04:21.661 --> 04:22.923
I said I am all right.

04:23.263 --> 04:27.495
I've really tried to reach you,
you've been always on my mind.

04:27.700 --> 04:31.932
But no one knows
your whereabouts.

04:33.106 --> 04:34.596
I'm sorry.

04:37.243 --> 04:40.542
It's more difficult than I thought

04:41.147 --> 04:43.411
to gather friends after 20 years past.

04:43.516 --> 04:44.244
Yeah, right

04:44.350 --> 04:45.908
Just if I knew where you...

04:46.019 --> 04:47.680
I said I am OK, I mean it.

04:51.057 --> 04:52.490
Don't worry about me, any more.

04:53.893 --> 04:55.724
We need to break the ice, here.

04:58.231 --> 05:00.563
May I sing a song?

05:00.700 --> 05:02.964
