08:05.485 --> 08:07.248
Do you remember
where that guy used to work?

08:07.520 --> 08:09.818
He'd worked for Tae-hwa Elec.,
before joining the army.

08:10.022 --> 08:12.217
It's passed 20 years since then.

08:12.458 --> 08:15.222
Oh, my face turns red badly!

08:15.328 --> 08:19.662
You've got autumn leaves
in this spring day.

08:19.899 --> 08:21.696
- Looks wonderful.
- Looks wonderful.

08:23.669 --> 08:26.467
Look at that! Shouldn't
we try to get him down?

08:26.572 --> 08:28.699
Leave him alone.
He should stop in time.

08:28.808 --> 08:30.799
- You're right.
- It's dangerous.

08:30.910 --> 08:32.775
Let him down.

08:32.945 --> 08:39.077
- Come down!
- Come down, have a drink!

08:43.556 --> 08:45.524
Come down, I say!

08:46.626 --> 08:50.585
- Do something!
- A train's coming! Hurry down!

08:50.663 --> 08:53.791
- Hey! Hurry down! Danger!
- Don't care about him any more.

08:54.033 --> 08:58.470
- Hey! Hurry down!
- It's a train! Hurry down.

08:58.838 --> 09:01.534
- Kim Youngho!
- He won't hear us.

09:01.641 --> 09:05.407
- Come down, you bastard!
- Hurry down, please.

09:05.478 --> 09:09.608
Don't worry. Ten to one
who went to Han river

09:09.815 --> 09:12.010
with suicidal intent didn't die.

09:12.118 --> 09:13.779
Kim Youngho!

09:14.554 --> 09:16.852
Kim Youngho, come down!

09:33.573 --> 09:36.804
That man is too much!

09:37.076 --> 09:40.637
- Hey! Hurry down, you bastard!
- I gave up.

09:40.746 --> 09:43.510
You win. Do as you like,
you crazy fool!

09:43.683 --> 09:45.310
Let's dance.

09:47.320 --> 09:49.845
Let's liven up!

09:55.861 --> 10:00.298
Hey! Come down!

10:01.133 --> 10:06.400
What is the matter?
Come down and have a talk.

11:03.929 --> 11:09.561
Kim Youngho.

11:12.805 --> 11:14.932
Kim Youngho!

11:27.687 --> 11:33.216
I am going back!

12:13.099 --> 12:15.201
The Camera

12:15.201 --> 12:19.570
The Camera
Three Days Ago, Spring 1999

12:20.339 --> 12:22.603
It's a group formed
when we worked in factory.

12:22.675 --> 12:26.042
Aha, that's the association
named Bongwoo club, Right?

12:26.112 --> 12:28.637
Right, so we decide to reunite
for the first time

12:28.914 --> 12:30.472
in about 20 years

12:30.583 --> 12:32.312
- To go on a picnic.
- Did you say a picnic?

12:32.418 --> 12:35.387
Yes. That's why I am calling
to you, to announce this event.

12:35.488 --> 12:37.115
Then, you chose the right place

12:37.223 --> 12:40.056
to give notice to your members.

12:40.126 --> 12:41.093
Thank you.

12:41.160 --> 12:42.923
I hope all of your members

12:43.729 --> 12:45.219
listen to this program

12:45.297 --> 12:47.060
and join the picnic.

12:47.433 --> 12:49.301
- Are you ready?
- Yes.

12:49.301 --> 12:50.996
OK. Start.

12:51.604 --> 12:53.868
The members of Bongwoo club

12:53.939 --> 12:55.964
who lived in Garibongdong

12:56.041 --> 12:58.771
20 years ago,

12:59.145 --> 13:01.613
are to meet together this time,

13:01.680 --> 13:03.511
to go on a picnic to the place

13:03.582 --> 13:06.107
Where we first had an excursion.

13:06.185 --> 13:07.709
So, Bongwoo club members

13:07.787 --> 13:11.553
listening to this program, please...

14:02.308 --> 14:04.401
- Are you from Seoul?
- Yes.

14:04.577 --> 14:06.511
I'm here to sell you the goods.

14:07.913 --> 14:11.542
- Money first please.
- Let me see the goods first.

14:12.785 --> 14:15.515
Here it is. Money first.

14:15.588 --> 14:17.146
Give it to me, you bastard!

14:47.987 --> 14:51.115
Not expensive for a thousand won.

14:51.590 --> 14:54.058
It costs a fifteen hundred

14:54.260 --> 14:57.127
at that rest area down below,
but the scenery's better here.

14:57.229 --> 15:00.630
You're right.
The scenery is to die for,

15:00.833 --> 15:02.596
and this coffee is really delicious.

15:05.104 --> 15:07.436
Wait a sec...

15:09.508 --> 15:11.874
Oh no, something's wrong!

15:12.144 --> 15:13.008
What?

15:13.145 --> 15:15.375
I forgot to bring money with me

15:15.547 --> 15:18.311
except credit cards.

15:18.417 --> 15:21.818
- What should I do?
- Look again, carefully.

15:21.887 --> 15:25.345
I forgot to draw some money
from the bank.

15:25.724 --> 15:27.316
I am so sorry.

15:27.526 --> 15:30.017
You won't believe me
to pay back next time, will you?

15:32.131 --> 15:33.894
Here, let me return this to you.

15:37.036 --> 15:39.231
It's already become useless.

15:41.907 --> 15:44.933
- Go ahead, have the rest.
- Thank you.

15:45.177 --> 15:47.338
I promise you
to pay for it next time.

15:48.247 --> 15:50.772
Look and smile.
Say Kim-chi.

15:51.951 --> 15:54.852
- Excuse me.
- One, two, three!

17:36.288 --> 17:38.722
- Good afternoon, sir.
- Hi.

18:34.546 --> 18:37.515
Uh... Kim!

18:38.117 --> 18:39.778
What are you doing?

19:12.417 --> 19:16.786
Are you the owner of this car?

19:17.256 --> 19:18.223
Yes.

19:18.790 --> 19:21.088
You're not allowed to park here.

19:21.426 --> 19:22.916
Your driver's license, please.

19:23.762 --> 19:28.096
- Show me your driver's license.
- This isn't my car.

19:28.167 --> 19:31.068
You said it was your car.

19:31.970 --> 19:33.733
This isn't a stolen car, is it?

19:34.173 --> 19:38.576
- Take out your identification card!
- What for?

19:38.644 --> 19:40.544
Your identification card,
right this moment!

19:51.190 --> 19:53.522
Stop! Stop there!

20:03.235 --> 20:06.500
- Who is it?
- It's me.

20:19.384 --> 20:20.442
Why are you here?

20:25.524 --> 20:27.219
Saemin?

20:28.660 --> 20:29.957
She's asleep.

20:34.299 --> 20:37.029
I asked why you came
without any reason.

20:42.708 --> 20:46.610
Poppy. I wanted to see Poppy.

20:56.054 --> 20:58.022
Poppy...

21:10.435 --> 21:14.166
That's enough, now.
Poppy! Go! Get back in!

21:20.178 --> 21:24.512
Why? Why?

22:50.635 --> 22:52.159
Kim Youngho.

22:57.242 --> 22:59.039
You're Kim Youngho, right?

23:07.786 --> 23:09.913
Move there.
I'll try it.

23:16.595 --> 23:19.462
Why are you carrying
so many keys like these?

23:28.240 --> 23:29.605
Now, you can get in.

23:50.896 --> 23:52.193
Come on in!

24:11.516 --> 24:13.746
Have a seat. Apologies for
such shabby hospitality.

24:19.357 --> 24:22.758
It was a difficultjob
tracking you down.

24:24.029 --> 24:26.657
It's leaking in a new place.
Last night, the rain fell on

24:27.199 --> 24:30.066
my forehead, as I lay in bed.

24:32.337 --> 24:35.033
You, sit down! Fucker!

24:37.008 --> 24:39.408
This isn't a game, sit!

24:47.285 --> 24:49.810
Isn't the way I live pathetic?

24:52.190 --> 24:54.920
Wonder why I live this way?

24:57.562 --> 25:03.626
Although I don't know
who sent you,

25:03.835 --> 25:05.928
I want to talk with you.

25:06.938 --> 25:10.032
It's a good mood, isn't it?

25:11.576 --> 25:13.339
Want a drink?

25:16.047 --> 25:19.175
But there's no booze here.

25:21.720 --> 25:26.589
With the last bit of
my money, I bought this.

25:26.791 --> 25:29.259
To kill just one guy with.

25:31.763 --> 25:34.459
I don't want to die alone.

25:34.833 --> 25:38.394
I need one bastard to come with me.

25:39.271 --> 25:43.139
Just one bastard among
all that ruined my life.

25:45.043 --> 25:46.806
But then...

25:47.612 --> 25:49.705
Who should I kill?

25:50.849 --> 25:53.909
It gives me hard time, you know

25:55.253 --> 26:00.850
Pick just one is hard thing to do.

26:02.060 --> 26:04.095
The fucking stock broker

26:04.095 --> 26:07.360
who made me go clean broke?

26:07.599 --> 26:09.726
The vampire like loan shark that

26:09.801 --> 26:11.826
charged the ridiculous interest?

26:11.903 --> 26:13.302
Or...

26:14.472 --> 26:17.464
How about the business partner

26:18.443 --> 26:21.173
who run away with my money?

26:29.588 --> 26:31.385
Or should I take my ex-wife

26:38.096 --> 26:40.064
and my kid

26:41.466 --> 26:43.525
to die with me?

26:44.603 --> 26:47.663
There're so many fuckers

26:47.806 --> 26:51.037
in my life that it's hard to

26:52.077 --> 26:54.443
pick just one.

26:55.814 --> 26:56.974
You!

27:01.152 --> 27:03.643
I don't know why you're here.

27:04.055 --> 27:06.250
This isn't just your day.

27:10.061 --> 27:11.289
Choose!

27:12.697 --> 27:15.564
Want to watch? Or leave now?

27:25.777 --> 27:29.508
You know Yun Sunnim, don't you?

27:32.250 --> 27:33.342
Who?

27:36.054 --> 27:40.514
Yun-Sun-lm.
I was sent by her.

27:43.094 --> 27:44.994
Who is Yun Sunnim?

27:46.031 --> 27:48.261
Don't you remember?

27:50.035 --> 27:52.265
You two...

27:56.408 --> 27:58.638
liked each other before.

28:00.078 --> 28:04.845
Oh! Yun Sunnim.

28:07.218 --> 28:09.550
But why is she looking for me?

28:10.722 --> 28:12.212
Who are you?

28:12.424 --> 28:16.520
I'm her husband.

28:17.529 --> 28:19.258
She wants to...

28:25.704 --> 28:28.366
...see you.

28:30.108 --> 28:32.576
You're joking, right?

28:34.813 --> 28:37.304
Why does she want to see me?

29:06.277 --> 29:08.245
Will you do me a favor?

29:10.048 --> 29:11.242
What is it?

29:11.483 --> 29:14.816
I bought some clothes this morning.

29:15.120 --> 29:17.145
I hope they fit you well, Mr. Kim.

29:18.223 --> 29:21.192
You're saying
I should wear this?

29:24.596 --> 29:27.463
You wanna put me in trouble, huh?

30:27.859 --> 30:29.417
What's that?

30:29.661 --> 30:32.289
Can't be going to see someone
in the hospital empty handed.

30:39.504 --> 30:42.337
Want one?

30:42.473 --> 30:48.207
It's a peppermint candy.
Really delicious.

31:11.135 --> 31:12.534
What's wrong?

31:18.576 --> 31:21.272
I was told that she lost
her conscious this morning.

31:28.753 --> 31:31.847
She could even talk to me last night.

31:34.626 --> 31:36.491
Too late.

31:42.800 --> 31:44.791
I know, but...

31:46.871 --> 31:49.066
I want to see her face, though.

32:41.125 --> 32:44.686
Honey, Youngho has come.

33:11.089 --> 33:12.989
Sunim...

33:16.194 --> 33:17.786
It's been a long time.

33:39.784 --> 33:43.185
Do you remember this?
Peppermint candy.

33:45.423 --> 33:49.860
When I was in the army,
You sent these to me.

33:50.628 --> 33:54.120
You put a candy in every letters.

33:56.401 --> 34:02.033
I've saved them.

34:04.375 --> 34:06.206
In fact...

34:08.312 --> 34:12.646
I got in trouble owing to them.

34:13.217 --> 34:17.949
As you sent back then...

34:23.261 --> 34:24.489
Look!

34:27.431 --> 34:29.661
They're still in the same shape.

34:40.244 --> 34:42.109
I'm sorry, Sunnim.

35:32.029 --> 35:33.360
Kim Youngho!

35:33.598 --> 35:34.929
Kim Youngho!

35:38.236 --> 35:40.602
I forgot to give something to you.

35:41.973 --> 35:43.608
She wanted me to give you this.

35:43.608 --> 35:45.735
She said it's not hers, but yours.

35:46.844 --> 35:49.836
She also said she was
just keeping it for you.

36:10.735 --> 36:15.832
It's so old. Nobody uses
a 20 years old camera.

36:16.741 --> 36:18.766
Think who wants to use
a manual camera these days?

36:18.943 --> 36:22.538
- How much can you give me?
- I will pay for 30,000 won.

36:27.018 --> 36:31.717
How can you fix just 30,000 won?

36:31.856 --> 36:33.790
You'd better look for another shop.

36:36.894 --> 36:41.024
- How about 50,000 won?
- 40,000 won. It's the maximum.

36:45.670 --> 36:46.830
Okay, then.

37:10.194 --> 37:12.754
Hey, Mr.!

37:13.631 --> 37:16.657
Film in the camera.
Take it back!

38:47.591 --> 38:49.660
Life is Beautiful

38:49.660 --> 38:54.029
Life is Beautiful
Summer 1994

38:59.003 --> 39:01.665
Miss Lee? You came early.

39:02.173 --> 39:03.800
No phone calls yet?

39:05.443 --> 39:06.535
Who?

39:08.212 --> 39:09.645
And so...

39:11.082 --> 39:14.051
Why do they want to be paid

39:14.118 --> 39:16.143
before giving us the goods?

39:16.420 --> 39:18.081
If he calls, refuse it.

39:18.956 --> 39:23.916
No. I'd better take care of it. What?

39:25.029 --> 39:27.190
Why are you saying like that?

39:28.766 --> 39:32.395
What? I can't talk to you that way?

39:36.874 --> 39:42.039
My business dull now a days.
It makes me crazy.

39:43.848 --> 39:46.373
Let's have a drink.

39:46.550 --> 39:50.680
I have to buy... No way,

39:50.955 --> 39:53.287
I should be the one
to buy you drinks...

39:54.325 --> 39:57.920
If you insist that way,
then I won't see you.

40:06.170 --> 40:08.468
She said she's going to get
a driving lesson.

40:10.441 --> 40:12.602
I don't know where.

40:15.413 --> 40:17.074
Anyway...

40:18.616 --> 40:23.053
Make sure she doesn't notice you,
When you're following her. Call me.

40:28.659 --> 40:31.355
Hey! Give me a cup of coffee.

40:31.429 --> 40:32.418
Yes, sir.

40:39.970 --> 40:44.839
Kim, what's making you feel good?
Have they gone up again?

40:45.743 --> 40:49.645
Tire has gone up by 300 won.

40:51.382 --> 40:56.081
300won's not a small amount at all.
You're making money at stocks

40:56.687 --> 41:00.555
as well as at your business.

41:04.795 --> 41:07.161
- Hey!
- Yes, sir?

41:07.598 --> 41:10.032
Who do you think, I am?

41:11.135 --> 41:12.329
You are the president.

41:12.503 --> 41:16.769
Right. I'm the owner. Then, why did you
brought coffee without a saucer?

41:19.343 --> 41:26.306
- I am sorry, sir.
- ¢Ü you've betrayed me...

41:26.383 --> 41:28.442
That's enough.

41:28.853 --> 41:30.821
Buy me a lunch!

41:30.921 --> 41:34.652
¢Ü betrayal of love...

41:36.927 --> 41:41.057
- Where should we go?
- Well, where should we go?

41:41.265 --> 41:44.098
- Wondang'll be difficult to be reached.
- Yeah, there must be congestion.

41:50.407 --> 41:52.204
Jesus, Are your keys ok?

41:52.510 --> 41:54.978
Why do you carry
so many keys?

41:55.346 --> 41:56.108
President!

41:56.280 --> 41:58.771
- Who? Me?
- No, Kim.

41:59.216 --> 42:01.207
- Phone calls for you.
- Who is it?

42:01.285 --> 42:05.221
- It's from the detective agency.
- Detective agency? Why?

42:05.623 --> 42:07.955
I think I can't eat out today.
Let me treat you a lunch next time.

42:08.025 --> 42:10.255
What are you talking about?

42:13.597 --> 42:17.055
Wait, wait. I'm going.

42:20.871 --> 42:22.133
Okay.

42:22.239 --> 42:25.231
Good, that's good! Oh, no! Stop it!

42:26.810 --> 42:30.769
I step on it, what am I gonna do?

43:04.381 --> 43:07.680
- Who is it?
- I ordered cigarettes.

43:08.586 --> 43:11.578
- What is it?
- Where is she, you bastard!

43:33.877 --> 43:36.744
Where do you think you're going!

43:47.625 --> 43:53.757
You fucker!

44:51.455 --> 44:53.082
Are you going home now?

44:55.392 --> 44:56.324
Yes.

44:59.897 --> 45:01.626
Aren't you going home?

45:01.865 --> 45:03.799
Later.

45:06.103 --> 45:07.730
How are you getting home?

45:14.511 --> 45:16.376
I can grab a taxi over there.

45:16.547 --> 45:17.946
Umm... okay

45:19.283 --> 45:20.614
Go then.

45:22.486 --> 45:24.078
Go.

45:25.823 --> 45:28.986
- Are you coming home early?
- No, I'll be late today.

46:01.992 --> 46:05.951
Where have you been keeping
a person waiting so long?

46:06.597 --> 46:08.997
Why didn't you go to eat?

46:09.600 --> 46:12.296
How can I enjoy a meal alone?

46:12.870 --> 46:15.430
- Didn't you have anything to eat, yet?
- Yes, I ate something.

47:09.326 --> 47:10.850
This tastes pretty good.

